<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="spare-no-expense-effort">spare no expense / effort</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不惜工本；全力以赴：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For the sake of the welfare of our offspring, we should spare no effort to protect our mother planet.
为了造福子孙后代，我们应不遗余力地保护我们的地球母亲。</p></div></div>